Power Generation Investco LLC Withdrawal from LouisianaGeneration Investco LLC We have been requested by EWSENA to file for withdrawal of Power Generation Investco LLCs qualification to conduct business in the State of Louisiana If you are aware of any reason NOT to withdraw from this state please advise me no later than Thursday June If we receive no objections we will proceed with withdrawal procedures Lillian R Bailey Administrator Corporate Services EBA Phone Fax
